cdata.name: ARK
cdata.desc:
Ark is a cryptocurrency platform built on top an improved Delegated Proof of Stake (DPoS) system derivedfrom Lisk, Crypti, and BitShares. It uses Smart Bridges to communicate with other (new and existing) blockchains to further increase its reach, providing a wider range of features in a single place.

Ark plans to stimulatecryptocurrency mass adoption by offering multipleconsumer tools like a card network, game tokens, anonymous transactions, multi-signature accounts, and others. Adding more features and tools along the way.
